{"word":"G4203 - πορνεύω - porneúō - porn-yoo'-o - Commit","sections":[{"paragraph":"<strong>மூல வார்த்தை / Original: </strong><span class=\"hebrewOrGreek\">πορνεύω</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>எழுத்துமாற்றம் / Transliteration: </strong><span class=\"transliteration\">porneúō</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>ஒலிபெயர்ப்பு / Phonetic: </strong><span class=\"phonetic\">porn-yoo'-o</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>சுருக்க விளக்கம் / Short Definition: </strong><span class=\"short-definition\">Commit</span>"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"parts-of-speech\"><strong>இலக்கண சொல்வகை / Part(s) of speech: </strong>Verb / வினைச்சொல்</span>"},{"paragraph":"வினைச்சொல் - வேசித்தனம் பண்ணு. வேசித்தனஞ்செய்"},{"paragraph":"1. to prostitute one's body to the lust of another"},{"paragraph":"2. to give oneself to unlawful sexual intercourse: to commit fornication"},{"paragraph":"3. by a Hebraism metaphorically, to be given to idolatry, to worship idols"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"original-in-english\"><strong>ஆங்கில மூலம் / Original in English: </strong>From <a href=\"#/G4204 - πόρνη - pórnē - por'-nay/4204\">G4204</a>; to <i>act</i> the <i>harlot</i>, that is, (literally) <i>indulge</i> unlawful <i>lust</i> (of either sex), or (figuratively) <i>practise idolatry:</i> - commit (fornication).</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>தொடர்புடைய எண்கள் / Cognate: </strong><a href=\"#/G1608/1608\">G1608</a>, <a href=\"#/G4202/4202\">G4202</a>, <a href=\"#/G4203/4203\">G4203</a>, <a href=\"#/G4204/4204\">G4204</a>, <a href=\"#/G4205/4205\">G4205</a>"}]}